data.description: Stunning two story home with unforgettable features! This exquisite home is perfect for those seeking luxury and convenience. With its unique decor and special touches, this residence is truly one-of-a-kind! This property offers an  combination of antique charm and modern amenities. The grand living room features a magnificent window wall that looks directly into the oasis of a backyard featuring 2 decks, a stunning pool with a 3 waterfall feature, hot tub, cabana with a bar and green egg grill area. Inside you will also enjoy a spacious den to entertain. The master suite is a sanctuary of its own with spacious layout and large private bath. Detached 3 car garage with game room above garage.
